Package boundary.ui

Class ApplicantUI

java.lang.Object
boundary.ui.ApplicantUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
ApplicantMenu, CommonMenu
public class ApplicantUI extends Object implements ApplicantMenu
The ApplicantUI class implements the ApplicantMenu interface and handles the user interface for an applicant. It provides the applicant with various options such as viewing available projects, applying for projects, submitting and editing enquiries, and more.
